lefExtendCellObsShapeUnderTrim(25.10)    lefExtendCellObsShapeUnderTrim(25.10)

Name
       lefExtendCellObsShapeUnderTrim

Syntax
       lefExtendCellObsShapeUnderTrim <listOfRoutingLayers>

       Type: String

       Default: ""

       Specifies a list of routing layers. On each specified layer the LEF OBS
       shapes  that are overlapped partially by a shape on the TRIMMETAL layer
       (that trims the routing layer), will be extended in the preferred rout-
       ing direction to be fully covered by the trim shape. You can  use  this
       global  for some advanced node libraries to avoid trim/OBS short viola-
       tions.

